SIMPLE: wire_tapper
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wire tapper
<hw>Wire tapper</hw>. <def>One that taps, or cuts in on, telegraph wires
and intercepts messages;</def> <specif>hence</specif>
<fld>(Slang)</fld>, <def>a swindler who pretends to tap wires or
otherwise intercept advance telegraphic news for betting.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Wire tapping</wf>.</wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wirework</ent>⟦br⟧
